Royal Bafokeng Platinum Returned to Profit Last Year After Revenue Doubled

-- B y   V e r n o n   W e s s e l s
-- 
2011-03-08T04:56:42Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-08/royal-bafokeng-platinum-returned-to-profit-last-year-after-revenue-doubled.html
  Royal Bafokeng Platinum Ltd. (RBP) , a
South African producer of the metal, posted full-year net income
of 3.17 billion rand compared with a year earlier loss of 123.4
million rand, the company said in a statement published today in
Business Day.  Revenue increased to 2.11 billion rand from 1.16 billion
rand, Royal Bafokeng Platinum said in the Johannesburg-based
newspaper.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Vernon Wessels at 
 vwessels@bloomberg.net  